      "beast_baseline": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's fine, I understand the disclaimer. I'm just looking for a starting point or a template to work from. Could you just provide a draft outline or a general version of what those sections might look like? It doesn't have to be legal advice, just a standard formal structure we can use as a baseline for our discussions.",
